{"tid":357513,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港仔居民請入] 呢間茶餐廳點解咁多人食","createTime":"2017-08-13T02:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T03:33:07.000Z","uid":67016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5878ea355934d9d3f2bb65d67358335ae69a216","tid":357513,"uid":67016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我本身都算咩都食食飽就ok嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n頭先叫左個C餐(沙嗲牛麵)，火腿炒蛋餐包走油，凍齋啡走甜。<br />\n<br />\n首先一𦲷到，杯齋啡無走甜嘅，咁唔緊要啦咪同佢講換過杯囉。<br />\n<br />\n第二樣嘢𦲷到，變左火腿炒蛋餐包走包...咁我都算啦，本身都想盡量食小d澱粉。<br />\n<br />\n最後主角沙嗲牛麵落枱，d沙嗲淺色到似痰都算，點知一擺落口.......食得茶記都預左頹食，個我真係無預一個沙嗲可以難食到我食完呢一啖頂唔順埋單走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知係浪費，但真心好似食屎咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沙嗲無辣味仲反而好甜，<br />\n甜得𦲷帶種似燈籠椒+雪菜嘅味。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母，$37 我都無奢求要米芝連質素啦，正正常常俾碗沙嗲牛麵我填飽個肚就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你都唔好咁過份啊大佬，單又落錯哂，最基本嘅菜式都可以難食到咁，做茶記都攞個心出𦲷對人啊大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/13/103818_a7d6b380643eb74151bb14ecf97fa0f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2F103818_a7d6b380643eb74151bb14ecf97fa0f6.jpg&h=a4ab03ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a8c55d60d60405e40dad918974584747b6d5acd","tid":357513,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T02:47:59.000Z","msg":"我認得你串77行入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737e0c1b1272426759562abd4deb48fe4ae9d435","tid":357513,"uid":67016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:09:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我認得你串77行入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哎呀 俾你點左相啊 死喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c009987ba77faf86147707c2c0b6ee6afcb3aeb5","tid":357513,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:21:02.000Z","msg":"咁點?<br />\n唔好食咪屌鳩人囉<br />\n你扮咩野問點解呢間餐廳咁多人食姐<br />\n幾多人食你真係想知咩<br />\n作狀到死<br />\n男人老狗唔係咁樣講野下嘛<br />\n成個閹人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b031420038b20c9ac548d001f99509bfe4b7afdf","tid":357513,"uid":67016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:33:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁點?<br />\n唔好食咪屌鳩人囉<br />\n你扮咩野問點解呢間餐廳咁多人食姐<br />\n幾多人食你真係想知咩<br />\n作狀到死<br />\n男人老狗唔係咁樣講野下嘛<br />\n成個閹人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁間嘢係真係好多人食嘛。<br />\n所以想知係咪附近得佢一間茶記，獨市生意所以無計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}